    <section class="v3-section v3-voice" id="voice">
      <div class="v3-inner">
        <div class="v3-heading"><h2>結果が出た後も続く、<br><strong>実際の通い方</strong></h2><p>MEMBER STORIES</p><div class="v3-lead">パーソナルとセルフの配分を変えながら、今も継続している会員様の実例です。</div></div>
        <div class="v3-voice-grid">{% for v in site.memberVoice.items %}{% if loop.index == 1 or loop.index == 3 or loop.index == 7 %}<article class="v3-voice-card"><div class="v3-voice-image"><img src="/{{ v.image }}" alt="{{ v.meta }}のビフォーアフター" loading="lazy"><span>{% if loop.index == 1 %}2か月で{% else %}{{ v.duration }}{% endif %}</span></div><div class="v3-voice-body"><small>{{ v.meta }}</small><h3>{{ v.story }}</h3><div class="v3-voice-result"><div><span>体重</span><strong>{{ v.weightKg }}<i>kg</i></strong></div><div><span>ウエスト</span><strong>{{ v.result }}<i>{{ v.unit }}</i></strong></div></div><ol class="v3-voice-route">{% for step in v.journey %}<li>{{ step }}</li>{% endfor %}</ol><div class="v3-voice-now">現在：{% for line in v.currentRoutine %}{{ line }}{% if not loop.last %}<br>{% endif %}{% endfor %}</div></div></article>{% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="v3-section v3-flow">
      <div class="v3-inner">
        <div class="v3-heading"><h2>無料体験までの流れ</h2><p>FREE TRIAL FLOW</p><div class="v3-lead">運動初心者の方も、トレーナーが一つずつサポートします。無理な勧誘は行いません。</div></div>
        <div class="v3-flow-grid">
          <article class="v3-flow-step"><span>01</span><img src="/images/v3-flow-counseling.jpg" alt="トレーナーによるカウンセリング" loading="lazy"><h3>受付・カウンセリング</h3><p>ご予約日時にご来店ください。続かなかった理由や、今回の目標を丁寧にお聞きします。</p></article>
          <article class="v3-flow-step"><span>02</span><img src="/images/v3-flow-assessment.jpg" alt="体組成測定" loading="lazy"><h3>体の状態を確認</h3><p>体組成や動き方を確認し、現在地と取り組む順番を分かりやすく整理します。</p></article>
          <article class="v3-flow-step"><span>03</span><img src="/images/personal1.jpg" alt="体験トレーニング" loading="lazy"><h3>体験トレーニング</h3><p>正しいフォームと、自分に合うメニューを実際に体験。疑問はその場で質問できます。</p></article>
          <article class="v3-flow-step"><span>04</span><img src="/images/v3-flow-plan.jpg" alt="食事写真を使ったプラン提案" loading="lazy"><h3>通い方をご提案</h3><p>生活と予算に合うプランをご案内します。体験後の入会は任意です。</p></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="v3-section v3-faq">
      <div class="v3-inner">
        <div class="v3-heading"><h2>よくあるご質問</h2><p>FAQ</p></div>
        <div class="v3-faq-list">{% for item in site.faq.items %}<article class="v3-faq-item"><button class="v3-faq-q" type="button"><span class="v3-faq-mark">Q</span><strong>{{ item.q }}</strong><span class="v3-faq-icon">＋</span></button><div class="v3-faq-a"><div><p>{{ item.a }}</p></div></div></article>{% endfor %}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="v3-final" id="final-cta">
      <video class="v3-final-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata" poster="/images/hero.jpg" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"><source src="/videos/final-cta.m4v" type="video/mp4"></video>
      <div class="v3-final-inner"><span class="v3-final-label">初回限定・完全無料</span><h2>もう一度始めるなら、<br><strong>今度は続けられる場所で。</strong></h2><p>パーソナルで覚えて、セルフで実践する。<br>あなたに合う続け方を、体験で一緒に見つけます。</p><a class="v3-offer-btn" href="#reserve"><span>初回<br>限定</span><b>無料体験を予約する</b> →</a><div class="v3-final-limit">先着順｜今月の体験予約枠 残り{{ site.campaign.remaining }}名様</div></div>
    </section>

    <section class="v3-reserve" id="reserve"><div class="v3-reserve-inner"><div class="v3-reserve-heading"><span>SELECT A DATE</span><h2>カレンダーから空き状況を確認</h2></div><div class="v3-reserve-widget"><iframe id="hacomono-widget-w0002" src="https://zennuwellnessdesign.hacomono.jp/widgets/2?isFilterableByCategory=false&isShowStudioInfo=true&studioIds=1" title="ZenNu 予約ウィジェット"></iframe></div></div></section>

    <section class="v3-access" id="access">
      <div class="v3-inner">
        <div class="v3-heading"><h2>上通アーケード内、<br><strong>通いやすい好立地。</strong></h2><p>ACCESS / CONTACT</p></div>
        <div class="v3-access-grid">
          <div class="v3-access-map"><iframe src="{{ site.access.mapEmbed }}" title="ZenNu WELLNESS DESIGNへのアクセス" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe></div>
          <div class="v3-access-info">
            <dl>{% for row in site.access.rows %}<div class="v3-access-row"><dt>{{ row.label }}</dt><dd>{{ row.value | safe }}</dd></div>{% endfor %}</dl>
            <div class="v3-contact-actions">
              <a class="v3-contact-btn is-line" href="{{ site.contact.lineUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span><small>24時間受付</small>LINEで問い合わせる →</span></a>
              <a class="v3-contact-btn is-tel" href="tel:{{ site.contact.tel }}"><span><small>電話で問い合わせる</small>{{ site.contact.telDisplay }}</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="v3-footer">
    <div class="v3-footer-inner">
      <div class="v3-footer-brand"><img src="/images/logo-yoko.png" alt="ZenNu WELLNESS DESIGN"><p>セルフ×パーソナルで、<br>続けることを当たり前にするジム。</p></div>
      <nav class="v3-footer-links" aria-label="フッターナビゲーション"><a href="#top">ページ上部</a><a href="#price">料金</a><a href="#access">アクセス</a><a href="{{ site.contact.lineUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LINE</a><a href="tel:{{ site.contact.tel }}">TEL {{ site.contact.telDisplay }}</a><a href="{{ site.footer.termsUrl }}">利用規約</a><a href="{{ site.footer.privacyUrl }}">プライバシーポリシー</a></nav>
      <div class="v3-footer-copy">{{ site.footer.copy }}</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="v3-sticky" id="v3-sticky"><div class="v3-sticky-inner"><div class="v3-sticky-copy">続け方を無料で相談</div><a href="#reserve"><span>初回限定</span><strong>無料体験を予約</strong><span>→</span></a></div></div>

  <script src="https://zennuwellnessdesign.hacomono.jp/js/widget.js"></script>
  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.v3-faq-q').forEach((button) => button.addEventListener('click', () => button.closest('.v3-faq-item').classList.toggle('is-open')));
    document.querySelectorAll('.v3-solution-slider').forEach((slider) => {
      const track = slider.querySelector('[data-v3-slider]');
      const cards = [...track.querySelectorAll('.v3-solution-card')];
      const dots = [...slider.querySelectorAll('.v3-slider-dots i')];
      let current = 0;
      const update = (next) => {
        current = Math.max(0, Math.min(cards.length - 1, next));
        track.scrollTo({ left: cards[current].offsetLeft - (track.clientWidth - cards[current].clientWidth) / 2, behavior: 'smooth' });
        dots.forEach((dot, index) => dot.classList.toggle('is-active', index === current));
      };
      slider.querySelector('[data-v3-prev]').addEventListener('click', () => update(current - 1));
      slider.querySelector('[data-v3-next]').addEventListener('click', () => update(current + 1));
      track.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
        const center = track.scrollLeft + track.clientWidth / 2;
        current = cards.reduce((closest, card, index) => Math.abs(card.offsetLeft + card.clientWidth / 2 - center) < Math.abs(cards[closest].offsetLeft + cards[closest].clientWidth / 2 - center) ? index : closest, 0);
        dots.forEach((dot, index) => dot.classList.toggle('is-active', index === current));
      }, { passive: true });
      update(0);
    });
    const sticky = document.getElementById('v3-sticky');
    const reserve = document.getElementById('reserve');
    const updateSticky = () => sticky.classList.toggle('is-hidden', window.scrollY < 320 || reserve.getBoundingClientRect().top < window.innerHeight);
    updateSticky();
    window.addEventListener('scroll', updateSticky, { passive: true });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
